			Its not rocket science people, all you have to do, is go to Unrest, go on the second floor and clear the spawn so the undead knight can spawn. that takes about 10min or so. then all you have to do is kill the craphole and he either drops the Bloodstained Tunic or Mantle. But I got this thing easy because my guild friend just gave me one when I got there.<BR>
